{"id":621833,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/11/【众人推】六四已逐渐在香港重演/","date":"2019-11-12T08:25:52Z","modified":"2019-11-12T09:16:22Z","title":"【众人推】“六四”已逐渐在三十年后的香港重演","content":"<p>警察镇压民众：</p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">【警、民口角期间，防暴警制服途人】<br />香港警察与民众之间关系持续恶化，有警员封锁行人天桥，有一名路过女子与警员口角期间，被警员喷射胡椒喷剂，该名女子尝试遮挡，反被多名警员压在地上制服。<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/%E8%AD%A6%E6%9A%B4?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#警暴</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/vzsBqIXvAh\">pic.twitter.com/vzsBqIXvAh</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; 自由亚洲电台 (@RFA_Chinese) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/RFA_Chinese/status/1194152793210118144?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">November 12, 2019</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/HKPoliceTerrorists?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#HKPoliceTerrorists</a> just pepper sprayed a pregnant woman squarely on her face, smashed her with batons, pressed her hard to the ground and cuffed her with force. That&#39;s insane. Hope that she and her baby are fine. <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/PoliceBrutality?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#PoliceBrutality</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/PoliceState?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#PoliceState</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/wxaLq3gMeg\">pic.twitter.com/wxaLq3gMeg</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; Demosistō 香港眾志 😷 (@demosisto) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/demosisto/status/1194124348040200192?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">November 12, 2019</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Hong Kong Police murdering protestors with his motorcycle.<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/HongKong?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#HongKong</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/U7P4JzrDbQ\">pic.twitter.com/U7P4JzrDbQ</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; Hong Kong Police Record (@hkpolicerecord) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hkpolicerecord/status/1193694161418932225?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">November 11, 2019</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<p>香港中环：</p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">今天，当勇武派出现在市中心商业区的时候，受到了英雄一般的热烈欢迎。<br />而此前，林郑月娥称：「抗争者是人民的敌人」</p>\n<p> <a href=\"https://t.co/rcCNNfMCh6\">pic.twitter.com/rcCNNfMCh6</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; 新闻大吐槽😷 (@TuCaoFakeNews) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/TuCaoFakeNews/status/1194144500781731840?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">November 12, 2019</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Riot police enter the Chinese University of Hong Kong <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/CUHK?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#CUHK</a> and give chase to protesters.</p>\n<p>Demonstrators are tackled and arrested as tear gas spreads in the campus <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/HongKongProtests?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#HongKongProtests</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#香港</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/luaToaXjKW\">pic.twitter.com/luaToaXjKW</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; Bloomberg TicToc (@tictoc) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/tictoc/status/1194160355812864000?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">November 12, 2019</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Riot police fire tear gas in Hong Kong’s Central business district and corner protesters <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/HongKongProtests?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#HongKongProtests</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#香港</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/csalI2lYDB\">pic.twitter.com/csalI2lYDB</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; Bloomberg TicToc (@tictoc) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/tictoc/status/1194156731854548992?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">November 12, 2019</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Some <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/HongKonger?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#HongKonger</a> working in <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/Central?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#Central</a> using their lunch hour to <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/protesting?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#protesting</a> . Have you ever seen this picture?<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/HongHong?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#HongHong</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/HongKongProtests?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#HongKongProtests</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/FreeHongKong?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#FreeHongKong</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/PassHKHumanRightsAndDemocracyAct?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#PassHKHumanRightsAndDemocracyAct</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/MQdojYJRGU\">pic.twitter.com/MQdojYJRGU</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; Kum.C LovE (@SOSHK831) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SOSHK831/status/1194128121928269824?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">November 12, 2019</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"tl\" dir=\"ltr\">Kong Girl！ <a href=\"https://t.co/W6SV2aK57s\">pic.twitter.com/W6SV2aK57s</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; 闾丘露薇 (@roseluqiu) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/roseluqiu/status/1194158872304345088?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">November 12, 2019</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<p>香港警察进入香港中文大学校园：</p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">歷史鏡頭：黑警向中文大學球場發射大量催淚彈鎮壓學生 <a href=\"https://t.co/3WR6PoMJSA\">pic.twitter.com/3WR6PoMJSA</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; 阿基里斯的黎明 (@panzerwong) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/panzerwong/status/1194160398041141248?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">November 12, 2019</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Earlier in <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/CUHK?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#CUHK</a> , scene on the sports ground as police fired tons and tons of teargas into the university campus. <a href=\"https://t.co/CkMVBmflzS\">pic.twitter.com/CkMVBmflzS</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; antiELAB (@anti_elab) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/anti_elab/status/1194172582053978113?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">November 12, 2019</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">An university &#8230;&#8230;&#8230;. <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/HongKongPolice?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#HongKongPolice</a> trun it to a war zone.<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/SOSHK?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#SOSHK</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/FreeHK?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#FreeHK</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/0ZvLwYinHV\">pic.twitter.com/0ZvLwYinHV</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; Alex (@AlexHhkppl) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/AlexHhkppl/status/1193788170338324481?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">November 11, 2019</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">香港警察襲襲 中文大學<br />只有恐怖分子才會對學校發動攻擊 <a href=\"https://t.co/zRCQdTvBfD\">pic.twitter.com/zRCQdTvBfD</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; ♆ ♆ BABAYAGA ♆ ♆ (@babayaga2_0) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/babayaga2_0/status/1194155424347377664?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">November 12, 2019</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">緊急</p>\n<p>全城支援中大，人、救護、各種物質（糧食、水、毛巾等等）</p>\n<p>大家幫忙轉 <a href=\"https://t.co/59rcK0qOn8\">pic.twitter.com/59rcK0qOn8</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; 鏟🐍人 (@Tonyworld15) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/Tonyworld15/status/1194152506999263232?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">November 12, 2019</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">the police has turned the cuhk campus into a battlefield. day two. <a href=\"https://t.co/orPoEXU420\">pic.twitter.com/orPoEXU420</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; lokman tsui 😷 (@lokmantsui) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/lokmantsui/status/1194157448593952769?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">November 12, 2019</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Police has been firing tear gas non stop in CUHK. More than 15 mins now. <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/antielab?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#antielab</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/hongkongprotests?src=hash&amp;ref_s