 dir=\"ltr\">Smoke coming out of <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/CUHK?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#CUHK</a>, the Chinese University of <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/HongKong?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#HongKong</a>, as riot police fired tear gas, clashed with students &amp; made rounds of arrests today inside campus.</p>\n<p>Video taken by the father of a friend who was strolling in Ma On Shan (and playing a sad song in background). <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/HK?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#HK</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/2CmGObCuls\">pic.twitter.com/2CmGObCuls</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; Carmen Ng 吳嘉文 (@Carmen_NgKaMan) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/Carmen_NgKaMan/status/1194170847243767808?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">November 12, 2019</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<p>香港街头抗争标语：</p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">时尚名店 Armani 前的大屏幕广告被示威者涂鸦，上面用英文写着 “他们开枪、他们谋杀、他们薪水不错”。 <a href=\"https://t.co/J9Nku6pgP1\">pic.twitter.com/J9Nku6pgP1</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; 美国之音香港 (@VOAHK) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/VOAHK/status/1193782866297180161?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">November 11, 2019</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<p>香港民众抗争故事：</p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">科大曾同学认为，香港变成如今局面，是因共产党只懂得强硬手段，不懂如何管制高智商人群！<br />太对了，就跟大陆无处不在的党委书记一样，专业狗屁不通，只懂与民为敌</p>\n<p>收买论被他驳斥的体无完肤，他认为只认钱的价值观是肤浅的，他们是为了民主自由的理念，89薪火在香港！<a href=\"https://t.co/kyEQIRZLJ7\">pic.twitter.com/kyEQIRZLJ7</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; 新闻大吐槽😷 (@TuCaoFakeNews) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/TuCaoFakeNews/status/1193702694835253248?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">November 11, 2019</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquot